    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Priscilla <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iva</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ibi</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audio</ex></expan> Martiniano <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>con</abbr><ex>iugi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXX et <expan><abbr>Claud</abbr><ex>iis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Decriano <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> et Mart<lb break="no" n="5"/>ino <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> fili<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes eine Nische mit den Büsten einer Frau, eines Mannes und zweier Kinder; in den Zwickeln darüber Trauergenien. Z. 5: spatium hinter AN. (B): Mander: Z. 3/4: Zeilenfall nicht angegeben; Balla - Buocz - Kádár - Mócsy - Szentléleky; AE 1972: Z. 4/5: et Mart/ino an(norum) doppelt.</p>
            </div>
